    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/f873f830b2ea0b7df11a65edc7bb4377.avif?t=1745582226\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/d7fc7228bc5a7563a60ec95fc56bdbb1.webp?t=1745582226\" width=119 height=42 /></span>       </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>At Death's Door</strong></i> <i>is a psychological horror game focused on exploration, atmosphere, and immersive storytelling. Set in the abandoned St. Valentine's Hospital, you play as a ghost hunter trying to save your career by uncovering its supernatural secrets. The game combines ghost-hunting mechanics, where you use specialized equipment to detect and record paranormal activity, with tense encounters that test your bravery. The added pressure to gather compelling evidence for your TV show brings urgency to the experience.</i> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/a818eed9fbfdc50450eeb4a1e63b6546.webp?t=1745582226\" width=181 height=30 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Non-Linear &amp; Supernatural Investigation Mechanics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/13aeeececef0333f55510260815947ff.poster.avif?t=1745582226\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/13aeeececef0333f55510260815947ff.webm?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/13aeeececef0333f55510260815947ff.mp4?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Evolving, Atmospheric &amp; Immersive Environments</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/b9bd83800f6f195e4f86558636dee6f4.poster.avif?t=1745582226\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/b9bd83800f6f195e4f86558636dee6f4.webm?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/b9bd83800f6f195e4f86558636dee6f4.mp4?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles and Minigames</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/6fea09fc1e0bfc827e66a46db0a023eb.poster.avif?t=1745582226\" width=280 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/6fea09fc1e0bfc827e66a46db0a023eb.webm?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/6fea09fc1e0bfc827e66a46db0a023eb.mp4?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/36252bca033e8461824fd9703a912fb6.poster.avif?t=1745582226\" width=280 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/36252bca033e8461824fd9703a912fb6.webm?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/36252bca033e8461824fd9703a912fb6.mp4?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore, investigate, and get to know the patients via notes and recordings</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/372bcdfe20e76e4ec4a8cdcf79c1d385.poster.avif?t=1745582226\" width=280 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/372bcdfe20e76e4ec4a8cdcf79c1d385.webm?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/372bcdfe20e76e4ec4a8cdcf79c1d385.mp4?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/047d4ff71f77fea7c7349d62032c8df4.poster.avif?t=1745582226\" width=280 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/047d4ff71f77fea7c7349d62032c8df4.webm?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/047d4ff71f77fea7c7349d62032c8df4.mp4?t=1745582226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Utilize ghost-hunting tools to find paranormal activity</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163470/extras/55d430b8951fe19a584d136d78ef3